	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div xml:id="div1" corresp="regest1">
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salve, mi venerande et optime <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Bullingere</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Constantiam</placeName> nuper, hoc est 26. augusti, cum bona <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l572" cert="high">Wirtempergensis</placeName> principis<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1"><persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p9708">Ulrich, Herzog von Württemberg</persName>.</note> gratia redii, nisi quod ille malignius ęquo mihi numeravit; nam tantum non 300 aureorum iacturam feci toto illo quadriennio, quo in ipsius ditione non ferendorum laborum molestia oppressus prorsumque enectus sum.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Et tamen gratias ago deo meo, quod bona conscientia illinc explicitus iam meis restituor.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Volui autem, licet occupatissimus, istuc tibi paucis indicare, quod sciam, quid amicorum meorum rumusculi iactitent, nempe irato me principe missum factum, ne desit, quod illis obiicias; nam quicquid hic peccavit princeps, non pro ira, sed pro consuetudine fecit<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2">Über die Entlassung <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Blarers</persName> am 30. Mai 1538 und deren unklare Hintergründe vgl. Martin <hi>Brecht,</hi> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosius Blarer</persName>s Wirksamkeit in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2481" cert="high">Schwaben</placeName>, in: Der <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l457" cert="high">Konstanzer</placeName> Reformator <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosius Blarer </persName>1492-1564. Gedenkschrift zu seinem 400. Todestag, hg. v. Bernd Moeller, <placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Konstanz</placeName>/<placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l496" cert="high">Stuttgart</placeName> 1964, S. 140-171, hier 166-168, und Theodor <hi>Pressel,</hi> <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosius Blaurer</persName>'s des schwäbischen Reformators Leben und Schriften, Stuttgart 1861, S. 437f. 441-444.</note>.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Sic enim solet.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero autem fore, ut olim per commodam aliquam occasionem, quod nunc desidero, benigne compenset et dignam principe munificentiam exerat, quum sit in me alioqui non iniquo animo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Commenda me clarissimis viris <persName ref="p8127" cert="high">Pellicano</persName>, <persName ref="p1753" cert="high">Leoni</persName><note xml:id="fn3" type="footnote" n="3"><persName ref="p1753" cert="high">Leo Jud</persName>.</note>, <persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodoro</persName><note xml:id="fn4" type="footnote" n="4"><persName ref="p8171" cert="high">Theodor Bibliander</persName>.</note> ac cęteris fratribus et amicis, quorum me precibus tuis quoque additis apud Christum iuvari vehementer cupio.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salutant te <persName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="p4082">Zviccii</persName><note xml:id="fn5" type="footnote" n="5"><persName ref="p4079" cert="high">Johannes</persName> und <persName ref="p4082" cert="high">Konrad Zwick</persName>.</note> cum germano meo fratre<note xml:id="fn6" type="footnote" n="6"><persName ref="p8178" cert="high">Thomas Blarer</persName>.</note> et sorore<note xml:id="fn7" type="footnote" n="7"><persName ref="p4320" cert="high">Margaretha Blarer</persName>.</note>.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale, mi plus quam charissime et optime frater.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l457" cert="high">Constantiae</placeName>, ultima augusti anno 1538.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosius Blaurerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse auf der Rückseite:]</note>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, Tiguricensis ecclesiae episcopo, domino et fratri observando atque charissimo etc.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
